window.bookSummaryJSON = "<p><b>Hailey </b></p> <p>What do you do when you find out your whole life was a lie? That your husband really wasn't your husband but someone else's? That the vows you made to each other were simply empty promises? </p> <p>You pick up and move to the country to start fresh. </p> <p>When life hands you limes, you make sure you have tequila because your life is about to get stirred up. </p> <p><b>Jensen </b></p> <p>I married my high school sweetheart, and the best thing she gave me was my baby girl. But we weren't enough for her. I wasn't enough for her. The last thing I expected on my birthday was a Dear John letter, but that’s what I got when she upped and left. </p> <p>Now, it's just me and my girl against the world - till a new girl moves in next door.</p>"; 
